### Change workshop status (M14)
### Allowed progression: BOOKED -> IN_PROGRESS -> READY -> COMPLETED, and any -> CANCELLED
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop/jobs/{{bookingId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Invalid status transition example (expect 409 INVALID_STATUS_TRANSITION)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop/jobs/{{bookingId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

{
  "status": "READY"
}

