### Refund any payment by id
### Response: 201 created, 200 idempotent replay, 409 REFUND_EXCEEDS_PAYMENT
### Permissions: MANAGER+
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/{{paymentId}}/refund
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{managerRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-manager

{
  "amountPence": 500,
  "reason": "Partial goodwill refund",
  "status": "RECORDED",
  "idempotencyKey": "refund-001"
}

### Payment detail (support/debug)
### Includes payment + refunds + linked sale/workshop booking
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/{{paymentId}}

### Get credit balance by identity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/credits/balance?email=alex.rider@example.com&phone=07111222333

### Issue credit manually
### Primary idempotency: required idempotencyKey (per credit account)
### Permissions: MANAGER+
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/credits/issue
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{managerRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-manager

{
  "email": "alex.rider@example.com",
  "phone": "07111222333",
  "amountPence": 1500,
  "notes": "Goodwill credit",
  "sourceRef": "MANUAL-CREDIT-001",
  "idempotencyKey": "credit-issue-001"
}

### Apply credit to sale/job checkout
### Primary idempotency: required idempotencyKey (per credit account)
### Secondary uniqueness guard: same account + target + amount returns 409 CREDIT_APPLICATION_CONFLICT
### Permissions: MANAGER+
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/credits/apply
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{managerRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-manager

{
  "saleId": "{{saleId}}",
  "email": "alex.rider@example.com",
  "phone": "07111222333",
  "amountPence": 1000,
  "notes": "Applying stored credit",
  "idempotencyKey": "credit-apply-001"
}

### Workshop payments report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/workshop/payments?from=2026-03-01&to=2026-03-31

### Workshop deposits report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/workshop/deposits?from=2026-03-01&to=2026-03-31

### Workshop credits report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/workshop/credits?from=2026-03-01&to=2026-03-31

### Audit query (MANAGER+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit?entityType=WORKSHOP_JOB&entityId={{bookingId}}&from=2026-03-01&to=2026-03-31&limit=100
X-Staff-Role: {{managerRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-manager

### M16: list workshop job parts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop-jobs/{{bookingId}}/parts
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

### M16: add workshop part line
### status USED immediately creates a WORKSHOP stock ledger deduction.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop-jobs/{{bookingId}}/parts
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 1,
  "status": "USED",
  "note": "Brake pads fitted"
}

### M16: update workshop part line
### status RETURNED creates a compensating stock ledger entry.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop-jobs/{{bookingId}}/parts/{{partId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

{
  "quantity": 2,
  "status": "USED",
  "note": "Used two items"
}

### M16: remove workshop part line
### Removing a USED line creates a compensating +stock ledger entry.
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop-jobs/{{bookingId}}/parts/{{partId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

{
  "note": "Part line removed"
}

### M16: workshop checkout now includes USED parts in saleTotal/outstanding
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop/jobs/{{bookingId}}/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

{
  "saleTotalPence": 5000
}

### M84: workshop job detail now includes partsOverview summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop/jobs/{{bookingId}}
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

### M84: parts list includes requirement summary, stock scope, and job parts status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop-jobs/{{bookingId}}/parts
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

### M84: reserve stock to the workshop job without consuming it yet
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop-jobs/{{bookingId}}/parts
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 1,
  "status": "PLANNED",
  "locationId": "{{locationId}}",
  "note": "Reserve one item for the job"
}

### M84: consume a reserved workshop part
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop-jobs/{{bookingId}}/parts/{{partId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

{
  "status": "USED",
  "locationId": "{{locationId}}",
  "note": "Part fitted"
}

### M84+: workshop dashboard exposes job-level partsStatus / partsSummary plus staffingToday
### optional staffDate override is useful for deterministic rota/workshop checks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop/dashboard?limit=20&staffDate=2026-03-10
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff
